## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias inherent in opinion pieces and essays. The complexity of the abortion debate means that not all perspectives can be fully captured in a brief report. Additionally, the data is current up to October 2023, and new developments in the legal and social landscape may influence future arguments and positions on abortion.